policy.</p></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Information We Collect</h3><ul class="mt-3 grid list-disc gap-2 pl-5"><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Personal Information: During registration, event sign-up, or other interactions, we collect personal details, such as your name, email address, phone number, home city, LinkedIn profile, photo, month of birth, and professional experience.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Automatic Information: We may collect non-personal information like browser type, operating system, IP address, and browsing behavior via cookies and similar tracking technologies.</li></ul></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">How We Use Your Information</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">We use the information collected for the following purposes:</p><ul class="mt-3 grid list-disc gap-2 pl-5"><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Event Registration and Communication: To manage event registrations, confirm attendance, and send SMS/email updates. To identify you when you communicate with the platform via SMS or email.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Community Building: To send members post-event review links and provide networking opportunities.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Service Improvements: To analyze usage data and improve the platform&#x27;s functionality.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Marketing: To inform you about upcoming events, updates, and offers. No mobile information will be sold or shared with third parties for promotional or marketing purposes</li></ul></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">How We Share Your Information</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">We are committed to maintaining your trust, and we want you to understand when and with whom we may share the information we collect.</p><ul class="mt-3 grid list-disc gap-2 pl-5"><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><i class="italic leading-[1.3]">Corporate affiliates.</i> We may share your information with our corporate affiliates that are subject to this policy.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><i class="italic leading-[1.3]">Business transfers.</i> We may share your information in connection with a substantial corporate transaction, such as the sale of a website, a merger, consolidation, asset sale, or in the unlikely event of bankruptcy.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><i class="italic leading-[1.3]">Legal purposes.</i> We may disclose information to respond to subpoenas, court orders, legal process, law enforcement requests, legal claims or government inquiries, and to protect and defend the rights, interests, health, safety, and security of Pew Research Center, our affiliates, users, or the public.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><i class="italic leading-[1.3]">With your consent or at your direction.</i> We may share information for any other purposes disclosed to you at the time we collect the information or pursuant to your consent or direction.</li></ul></li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve user experience, analyze traffic, and personalize content. You can control cookie settings in your browser, but disabling cookies may affect platform functionality.</p></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Data Security</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data. Despite our efforts, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Your Rights and Choices</h3><ul class="mt-3 grid list-disc gap-2 pl-5"><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Access and Correction: You can access and correct your personal information via your profile settings or by contacting us directly.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Deletion: You may request the deletion of your personal data by contacting us, but some data may be retained for legal or operational purposes.</li><li class="leading-[1.3] marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium">Opt-out: You can opt-out of marketing communications by following the unsubscribe instructions or contacting us.</li></ul></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Children’s Privacy</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">Our services are not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18.</p></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Changes to This Policy</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on our website, and significant updates will be communicated via email or an announcement. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p></li><li class="marker:font-plus marker:text-lg marker:font-medium"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.3]">Contact Us</h3><p class="mt-2 leading-[1.3]">For questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at<!-- --> <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#8bf8fefbfbe4f9ffcbcde4fee5efeef9c5eef3fef8a5e8e4e6"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="4734323737283533070128322923223509223f32346924282a">[email&#160;protected]</span>.</a></p></li></ol></div><p class="mt-7 text-lg leading-[1.3]">Thank you for being a valued member of the FounderNexus community!</p></div></section></main><div class="Toastify"></div><script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-8a4a2ada38e1f249.js" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"1:HL[\"/_next/static/media/02743a8d10a3d186-s.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/woff2\"}]\n2:HL[\"/_next/static/media/0560c261627a3561-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\n3:HL[\"/_next/static/media/0f9fe9e973978b55-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\n4:HL[\"/_next/static/media/1521282172f993a3-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\n5:HL[\"/_next/static/media/1e41be92c43b3255-s.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/woff2\"}]\n6:HL[\"/_next/static/media/40753d62591958a5-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\n7:HL[\"/_next/static/media/544d12a7997a9605-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\n8:HL[\"/_next/static/media/5626946253e54398.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/woff2\"}]\n9:HL[\"/_next/static/media/636a5ac981f94f8b-s.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/woff2\"}]\na:HL[\"/_next/static/media/6d3c16125be415e3-s.p.ttf\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/ttf\"}]\nb:HL[\"/_next/static/media/904be59b21bd51cb-s.p.woff2\",\"fon